last_episode_to_air.name: Done Patrol
last_episode_to_air.overview: After returning to Cloverton, the Doom Patrol gather for a final mission one that proves to be unlike any they’ve had before.

name: Doom Patrol
overview: The Doom Patrol’s members each suffered horrible accidents that gave them superhuman abilities — but also left them scarred and disfigured. Traumatized and downtrodden, the team found purpose through The Chief, who brought them together to investigate the weirdest phenomena in existence — and to protect Earth from what they find.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Set after the events of Titans, the Doom Patrol – consisting of Robotman, Negative Man, Elasti-Woman, and Crazy Jane, and led by Dr. Niles Caulder / The Chief – receive a mission from Cyborg that they cannot ignore and will change their lives.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In season two, the members of the Doom Patrol now find themselves mini-sized and stranded on Cliff’s toy race car track. Here they begin to deal with their feelings of betrayal by The Chief, while confronting their own personal baggage. And as each member faces the challenge of growing beyond their own past traumatic experiences, they must come together to embrace and protect the newest member of the family: Dorothy Spinner, Niles’ daughter, whose powers remain a mysterious but real threat to bringing on the end of the world.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: In season three, Dorothy’s confrontation with the Candlemaker leads to a devastating loss. The Doom Patrol is at a difficult crossroads and each member struggles to face who they are and who they want to be. And things get a whole lot more complicated when Madame Rouge arrives in a time machine with a very specific mission, if only she could remember it.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: The team unexpectedly travels to the future and finds an unwelcome surprise. Faced with their imminent demise, the Doom Patrol must decide once and for all which is more important: their own happiness or the fate of the world?

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: The reluctant heroes of the Doom Patrol – Robotman, Negative Man, Elasti-Woman and Crazy Jane face the threat of Mr. Nobody, who’s after The Chief.

episodes.name: Donkey Patrol
episodes.overview: Following Mr. Nobody’s capture of The Chief, the Doom Patrol investigate the mysterious albino donkey and discover it’s a door to another universe, where Mr. Nobody is in control.

episodes.name: Puppet Patrol
episodes.overview: The Doom Patrol set out for Paraguay where they discover the Nazi doctor who created Mr. Nobody and the connection between The Chief and the two villains.

episodes.name: Cult Patrol
episodes.overview: Willoughby Kipling conscripts the Doom Patrol into helping him avert the end of the world by stopping a nihilistic cult.

episodes.name: Paw Patrol
episodes.overview: With the Apocalypse in full swing, the Doom Patrol must work with an unlikely ally – and a very special pug – to stop the end of the world.

episodes.name: Doom Patrol Patrol
episodes.overview: Jane, Larry and Rita visit a school where the original Doom Patrol has retired. Meanwhile, Cliff & Vic bond over their mutual “father issues.”

episodes.name: Therapy Patrol
episodes.overview: After a violent outburst from Cliff, the team engages in some self-led group therapy – leading to some growth within the group as they are knit closer together.

episodes.name: Danny Patrol
episodes.overview: A sentient, gender-queer, teleporting street named Danny who’s being hunted by the secret Bureau of Normalcy needs help from Niles – but gets Vic and Larry instead.

episodes.name: Jane Patrol
episodes.overview: Jane retreats into The Underground, a treacherous place deep within her own mindspace, where she encounters her many personas and dark traumas of her past.

episodes.name: Hair Patrol
episodes.overview: Vic and Rita face a dangerous man called The Beard Hunter, who’s been activated by the Bureau of Normalcy to find Niles Caulder.

episodes.name: Frances Patrol
episodes.overview: While Larry pays a visit to his long-lost love, Cliff and Rita travel to Gator Country to reconnect with his daughter. Vic worries about his operating system.

episodes.name: Cyborg Patrol
episodes.overview: With Vic captured and held at the Ant Farm, his father hatches a plan with the rest of the Doom Patrol to break him out. Naturally, things go awry.

episodes.name: Flex Patrol
episodes.overview: The Doom Patrol tries to restore the memories and abilities of Flex Mentallo, while Rita confronts her self-doubt and Larry realizes how tied he is to the Negative Spirit.

episodes.name: Penultimate Patrol
episodes.overview: The Doom Patrol enter the Nobodyverse to save the Chief.

episodes.name: Ezekiel Patrol
episodes.overview: The Doom Patrol go their separate ways in the season finale.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: Set after the events of Titans, the Doom Patrol – consisting of Robotman, Negative Man, Elasti-Woman, and Crazy Jane, and led by Dr. Niles Caulder / The Chief – receive a mission from Cyborg that they cannot ignore and will change their lives.

episodes.name: Fun Size Patrol
episodes.overview: The Doom Patrol (along with Niles & his daughter) are still mini-sized after their last adventure. Ultimately, Niles will have to sacrifice something precious to save the team.

episodes.name: Tyme Patrol
episodes.overview: Cliff, Jane, and Rita pursue a time-altering doctor in their reluctant quest to help Niles and Dorothy. Meanwhile, Vic meets a military vet who challenges his beliefs.

episodes.name: Pain Patrol
episodes.overview: Niles, Rita, and Larry end up in the interdimensional clutches of Red Jack, an infamous villain who feeds on pain, while Cliff visits his daughter with Jane.

episodes.name: Sex Patrol
episodes.overview: When the Dannyzens throw a massive party at Doom Manor to resuscitate Danny the Brick, Dorothy longs to join the festivities and experience life as a grown-up. As the party rages on, Rita asks Flex Mentallo to help unleash her full potential -- which has some dangerously racy consequences.

episodes.name: Finger Patrol
episodes.overview: Dorothy finds a friend in Baby Doll, while Vic looks to win Roni back. With Rita’s help, Larry finally tries to break the ice with his family.

episodes.name: Space Patrol
episodes.overview: As Niles and Cliff set out to find a missing Dorothy, Larry is tasked with handling Niles’ old research team when the ageless aeronauts return from space.

episodes.name: Dumb Patrol
episodes.overview: While Niles heads north to find Dorothy’s mother, the Doom Patrol embraces their inner morons after receiving a mysterious package.

episodes.name: Dad Patrol
episodes.overview: While Jane sets out to prove her worth in The Underground, Cliff goes into “dad” mode and Niles devotes a day to Dorothy, who’s finally growing up.

episodes.name: Wax Patrol
episodes.overview: Before the Doom Patrol can answer a call to save the world from The Candlemaker in the season finale, they must first battle long-forgotten imaginary friends.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: In season two, the members of the Doom Patrol now find themselves mini-sized and stranded on Cliff’s toy race car track. Here they begin to deal with their feelings of betrayal by The Chief, while confronting their own personal baggage. And as each member faces the challenge of growing beyond their own past traumatic experiences, they must come together to embrace and protect the newest member of the family: Dorothy Spinner, Niles’ daughter, whose powers remain a mysterious but real threat to bringing on the end of the world.

episodes.name: Possibilities Patrol
episodes.overview: Dorothy and the Candlemaker finally face-off, while the Doom Patrol – now freed from their wax encasings – face troubling side effects. Rita holds the key, but is she ready to answer the call?

episodes.name: Vacay Patrol
episodes.overview: A relaxing vacation to escape the Doom Patrol’s recent loss proves anything but – especially when an unexpected evil lurks nearby.

episodes.name: Dead Patrol
episodes.overview: After waking up in the tunnel of souls, the Doom Patrol must confront their own personal purgatories. Back at the manor, Dorothy and Larry consult a highly specialized detective agency to help reach their friends.

episodes.name: Undead Patrol
episodes.overview: The newly “undead” members of the Doom Patrol are inspired to work on themselves. Later, the team is rocked by the arrival of a mysterious woman on a time machine – and a former foe.

episodes.name: Dada Patrol
episodes.overview: Madame Rouge enlists the Doom Patrol’s help after learning about her unsettling past. While the rest of the team works to infiltrate the target, Rita stays behind and finds a surprising connection with their mysterious friend.

episodes.name: 1917 Patrol
episodes.overview: Plunged back in time, Rita attempts to navigate the Bureau of Normalcy with help from an oddly familiar group. Meanwhile, Jane gives Kay her first taste of freedom, while Larry finds closure with his son.

episodes.name: Bird Patrol
episodes.overview: Vic consults an old friend for help with a major life change, Cliff takes his online habits too far, and Jane battles the “others” for Kay. Sensing imminent danger, Madame Rouge attempts to rally the highly distracted group.

episodes.name: Subconscious Patrol
episodes.overview: While the fog obscures more than just the air, Vic, Cliff, Jane, and Larry must relive their most shameful moments until a breakthrough occurs, and Rita begins to better understand Madame Rouge.

episodes.name: Evil Patrol
episodes.overview: With Madame Rouge vying for her old spot in the Brotherhood of Evil, the Doom Patrol brace themselves for their impending visit.

episodes.name: Amends Patrol
episodes.overview: As the Brotherhood of Evil closes in, the Doom Patrol try to set aside past issues in hopes of becoming a true superhero team – or risk being taken out for good.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: In season three, Dorothy’s confrontation with the Candlemaker leads to a devastating loss. The Doom Patrol is at a difficult crossroads and each member struggles to face who they are and who they want to be. And things get a whole lot more complicated when Madame Rouge arrives in a time machine with a very specific mission, if only she could remember it.

episodes.name: Doom Patrol
episodes.overview: As they struggle to function as a cohesive group, the Doom Patrol are confronted by a horrifying realization in the future.

episodes.name: Butt Patrol
episodes.overview: A desperate Doom Patrol strategize ways to wipe out the zombie butts… and reverse their grim future.

episodes.name: Nostalgia Patrol
episodes.overview: Larry and Jane seek new purpose in Keeg and Kay’s absence. Vic attempts to reconnect with his old crew. A mysterious invitation to a retrospective comes at the perfect time for a newly ousted Rita.

episodes.name: Casey Patrol
episodes.overview: When the safety of Danny and everyone housed within is compromised, Dorothy is forced to step up with some unexpected help.

episodes.name: Youth Patrol
episodes.overview: When Rita awakens unexpectedly aged, a mishandled spell teenage-ifies the Doom Patrol just as Willoughby asks for their help stopping the rise of Immortus and the end of the world as they know it.

episodes.name: Hope Patrol
episodes.overview: With the end of existence imminent, a determined Doom Patrol seek to get their longevities back and save the universe.

episodes.name: Orqwith Patrol
episodes.overview: As Jane ropes Cliff into longevity-hunting, Vic and Deric search for Larry, and Rouge tries to sway Rita into joining her on a trip to Orqwith.

episodes.name: Fame Patrol
episodes.overview: As Dorothy and Casey team up for a new mission, the Doom Patrol's pursuit of Immortus leads them to a superhero parade.

episodes.name: Immortimas Patrol
episodes.overview: After realizing they’re trapped in a continuous loop of music-filled Immortimas Days, the Doom Patrol confront the people they’ve become, while reckoning with who they once were.

episodes.name: Tomb Patrol
episodes.overview: After believing she’s uncovered the source of Immortus’ power, Rouge tries to convince the Doom Patrol to help excise it.

episodes.name: Portal Patrol
episodes.overview: Thrown into a time stream, the Doom Patrol have just one hour to find their longevities, rescue Rita, and save the world.

episodes.name: Done Patrol
episodes.overview: After returning to Cloverton, the Doom Patrol gather for a final mission one that proves to be unlike any they’ve had before.
